Un-gzip, untar and build from source tarball:

gzip -dc afile-X.X.X.tar.gz | tar xvf -
cd afile-X.X.X
./configure && make && make install

Now configure your openradiusd to make use of the afile instead of stock
ascfile module by editing the "configuration" file. Restart openradisud
daemon and watch its log file for possible error messages.
